{"tid":496668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日我最病】幫襯溫泉會館後發燒骨痛 數百人逼爆醫院","createTime":"2017-12-12T02:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T03:00:06.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0cd5849f31e8ad2af1976786a80c638437da650","tid":496668,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:14:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>【今日我最病】幫襯溫泉會館後發燒骨痛 數百人逼爆醫院</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501647/20171210_chinaR_99Y_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F3501647%2F20171210_chinaR_99Y_w.mp4&d=Wk6sw9ONsJJDxQCO8jxROleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8e9f8f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501647/20171210_chinaR_99Y_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n天氣轉冷，最好是浸溫泉！可是，數百人在吉林省遼源市光顧一間溫泉會館後，出現發燒、四肢無力、渾身酸痛、骨骼疼痛等症狀，湧到當地醫院求醫，逼爆醫院，醫院的醫護人員更穿上全套防護裝備。民眾質疑溫泉的水質有問題，溫泉已被勒令停業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/large/1512890773_1ca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Flarge%2F1512890773_1ca0.jpg&h=b6b8e12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/large/1512890771_73cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Flarge%2F1512890771_73cb.jpg&h=beb0c450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼源當地多間醫院，從上周五（8日）起被病人迫爆，有要入院的病人沒有病房，要睡在走廊，有受害者稱：「我們一家三口，周六早上開始冷後來熱全身難受，孩子晚上發燒 ，周日早上喝水都吐&hellip;&hellip;」，不少網民都說實在太恐怖了。<br />\n當局的通稿指，出現發燒等症的民眾，多是曾光顧一間名叫「碧海雲天溫泉會館」，雖然當局稱這間會館的衞生許可證、從業人員健康證齊全，可是民眾卻懷疑溫泉的水質有問題，「周二之去過的，沒有不發燒的人」。當局已經啟動公共衞生應急預案，除請專家、醫護人員病人治療，同時亦要求這溫泉停業，務求盡快找出事故原因。<br />\n新浪微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171210/57563772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57563772&d=Wk6sw9ONsJJDxQCO8jxROleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=9c32a95a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57563772&h=5d5585f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171210/57563772</a>"},{"pid":"0fc62173b507cffa6c583e89397bca8a8ed0619a","tid":496668,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"有人係池水度屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f59c6d3d40bcf3b81434c07b88bcf8170c670bb","tid":496668,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"浸污水"},{"pid":"3cac9489eab13f4e06f93520fa015f5610468edc","tid":496668,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"係大陸浸溫泉同自殺有咩分別"},{"pid":"08c178bf100a343f91cf19279c988b737655a594","tid":496668,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"化糞池當成溫泉, 唔病就奇"}]}